Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:03.37,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,A dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:05.62,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,A borderline of reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:09.88,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,is a dangerous and fragile abyss\Nof darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:14.09,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Be careful not to be consumed by a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:51.92,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No. A pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:57.05,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:57.84,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Feast of victims\NInmu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:17.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Last stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:19.97,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:22.76,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:34.92,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,The first night:\NI am being watched!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.88,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:01.84,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow\NI have to take a different train.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:24.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Just my imagination. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:46.26,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,A kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:50.06,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No. Someone was following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:17.21,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm sure someone is watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:32.18,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.56,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:36.36,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Spying on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:37.60,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:41.57,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It feels like someone is watching me\Nall the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:44.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a little paranoid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:45.70,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:48.82,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's one thing when you're outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:52.70,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,but in a classroom, under your skirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.58,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You watch too many weird videos?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.50,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I am serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:03.74,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Are you upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.22,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:18.40,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Paranoia?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:37.66,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Who's there? Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't loot at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.02,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.40,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Counseling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.57,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's close to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.62,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:22.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That one? I never noticed it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:43.44,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:49.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Come this my, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:51.70,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:56.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:07:01.21,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You feel like someone is\Nalways watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:06.84,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yes. Not always, but when I look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:11.84,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Some kind of phobia, I think,\Nfear of being watched, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:13.97,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:17.68,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You feel people's eyes on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:22.27,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,whether they're there or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:25.36,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:28.94,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:33.82,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I will let you have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:37.41,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,In that dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:41.00,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,you will discover all that you desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:46.25,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,In that dream,\Nyou will be free to be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:52.97,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,When you awake, you'll be yourself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:55.84,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,All I desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:02.23,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Have you ever stared at your own back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:03.35,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:07.27,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The truth is where you cannot see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:12.69,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Just as you cannot see your own back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:25.17,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Enjoy it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:27.58,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Your lusty dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.27,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.61,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It was so real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:39.24,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Was that the real me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:13.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.53,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:25.74,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:31.79,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.80,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No! Don t!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.48,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Not like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.49,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:04.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,More. More.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:27.93,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm coming. Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.64,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Now you know the real you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.15,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I have been watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:23.45,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I have been watching myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:47.34,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Your outside is the reverse of your inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.64,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What you desire is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:52.39,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,what you abhor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:04.42,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,The second night:\NThings detested
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:15.58,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,How many years\Nhave you been doing this job?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:19.25,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What is this?\NYour stitches are all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.50,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm s-s-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:25.92,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yamasawa! Do you want to ruin\Nthe Mikthara Brand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:28.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yamasawa again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:35.23,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yayoi gets tense before the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:40.86,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yamasawa is her stress reduction.\NGiven his character.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:45.32,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It was a sudden design change, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:49.57,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Your job is to deal with\Nminor design changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:53.74,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What a useless man!\NYou're lower than a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:57.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You dare look at me like that?\NYou're lower than a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:02.04,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't bother to come tomorrow. Or ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:04.21,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No, Ms. Yayoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:07.09,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Be a dog, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:10.84,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'll raise you\Nfrom lower than a dog to a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:12.89,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ms. Yayoi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:15.00,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:15.81,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:19.14,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You handle number 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.58,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:22.44,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.40,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:30.41,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Bow wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:37.70,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid? What a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:40.96,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Okay, everybody. Work, work!\NWe don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.46,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:46.50,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yamasawa, no more.\NDon't bother me, go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:50.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But, ma'am, you promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:52.89,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,From lower than a dog to a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:57.06,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm not so low to hire a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:01.48,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have hired a man like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:17.49,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,A fortune teller? Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:23.37,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're flipped inside out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:26.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.34,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Your outside is the reverse of your inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:33.97,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What you desire is what you abhor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:38.26,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You want to catch my attention\Nand take my money?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:41.73,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I hate fortune tellers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:49.48,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Have you ever stared at your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:02.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.22,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yamasawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:29.57,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.77,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:31.79,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Back off, back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:34.92,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Clear the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:39.89,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Did you check the outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:43.31,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,One needs size adjustment,\Nthe rest is all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:47.56,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,All right.\NI'll do the final check at the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:50.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hey, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:53.65,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Too much color, it'll kill the lighting.\NPaint again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:58.15,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But tomorrow's the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:18:02.16,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You'll work overnight. I'm the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:06.00,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.80,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. What am I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:33.31,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yamasawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:40.61,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yamasawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:45.03,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yamasawa! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:53.33,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I want that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:02.93,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.22,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yamasawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:12.10,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ms. Yayoi, it's show time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:20.61,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can get away with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.24,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:35.25,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:40.42,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No. Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:49.89,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Stop. Please. Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.95,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What are you staring at?\NSomeone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:27.64,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Yamasawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yamasawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.31,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What're you forgetting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:35.52,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yamasawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:42.86,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,A hog like you has no business\Nsaying my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:52.37,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That was close. I almost chopped it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:01.46,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ms. Yayei of the Mikihara Brand is\Npeeing on herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:05.68,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,How dare you talk to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:08.80,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's wet. You'll catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:12.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No, not that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.64,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,This side, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:27.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No! Don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:35.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You know what to do, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:38.46,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:41.92,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You just don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.80,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You suck if.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:49.22,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Or the scissors will do their work\Non your pretty face.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:08.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Not bad. Keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:23.79,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Good. More. Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:32.68,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Now, a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:42.56,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Please. Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:48.24,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NWe've only just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:23:01.62,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're drenched, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.38,0:23:03.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.84,0:23:05.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Feels good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:09.88,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You get tormented, humiliated,\Nand you get wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:11.26,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:14.97,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well, if it doesn't feel good...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:19.23,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No. Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.15,0:23:29.24,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's getting good.\NYou've been using it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.36,0:23:30.90,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:35.95,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,See, ma'am, you're like this down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.04,0:23:42.33,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.00,0:23:45.92,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.34,0:23:50.21,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Please what? Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.13,0:23:53.34,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.80,0:23:56.39,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:23:58.89,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I want your...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.14,0:24:01.18,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,My what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.39,0:24:05.52,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I want your hard one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.27,0:24:11.94,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I see. You want it that much?\NThen I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.42,0:24:30.84,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's good. I feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:33.92,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're driving me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.11,0:24:53.24,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm coming. I'm coming again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.99,0:25:04.08,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,More. Give me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.52,0:25:29.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's so good, Yamasawa.\NI underestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.90,0:25:32.23,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yamasawa...